articles.title: 'It’s like I don’t do the same sport' - Breakaway describes being passed by Pogačar and Vingegaard at Tour de France - Cyclingnews
articles.description: 'You want to hate them, but they are cool guys and make cycling fun to watch' says Tobias Halland Johannessen
articles.content: “When those two guys went past, it’s like I don’t do the same sport as them” is how Tobias Halland Johannessen (Uno X-Mobility) described being passed by Tadej Pogačar (UAE Team Emirates) and Jonas V… [+3497 chars]
